    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is a practical choice for a buyer seeking inexpensive transportation or a project opportunity. It offers solid value for the money, a clean, straightforward presentation, and the chance to own at a very accessible price point. An affordable way to get on the road without overcommitting.",
