      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little runner with plenty of life left for the right person. It\u2019s not a showroom car, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who needs affordable wheels, a handy project, or a dependable backup to have around. Easy on the wallet and priced to move, with the kind of character that makes used cars feel worth owning.",
      "price": 4800.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly project or workhorse with strong value for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at. This car shows its age cosmetically, but it has the kind of straightforward mechanical layout that makes it appealing for a hands-on owner. Good candidate for a commuter build, parts donor, or weekend revival, with usable power delivery and a chassis that still offers plenty of potential. If you want an inexpensive car you can tinker with and put to work, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap entry. Runs, rough, priced to move. Great fixer or parts car. First serious buyer takes it.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of lived-in character you can\u2019t fake\u2014a true diamond-in-the-rough for someone who sees possibility where others just see age. It\u2019s an affordable way into ownership with plenty of personality, perfect for a handy driver, a project seeker, or anyone who appreciates a machine with stories already written and room for a few more. If you want something with presence, potential, and a price that leaves room to make it your own, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "A practical, budget-friendly vehicle that offers dependable basic transportation and excellent value for the price. Ideal for a first-time buyer, commuter, or anyone seeking an affordable car with honest character. A smart opportunity to get on the road for less.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Reliable transportation doesn\u2019t have to break the bank. This car is a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants an affordable daily, a backup vehicle, or a project to tinker with. It\u2019s being offered honestly and priced to make sense, with plenty of life and usefulness left for the right buyer. If you want something straightforward, approachable, and easy on the wallet, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Solid opportunity for someone looking for an inexpensive driver or light project. This car shows its age cosmetically and is being sold in poor condition, but it still offers a strong, proven platform with serviceable mechanicals and good potential. Engine starts up, drivetrain pulls as it should, and it has the kind of straightforward, durable setup that makes it appealing for a commuter, backup vehicle, or weekend fixer. Not a showpiece, but a practical buy for someone who values function and mechanical simplicity over cosmetics. Priced to move and worth a look if you want affordable transportation with upside.",
      "price": 5950.0,
